    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the beef ragù is cooking, strip the <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them finely, discard the stems</p><p>Chop the <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the <strong>stalks</strong></p>",
